We loved this dish! Three forks is good for me! I made the tomatillo sauce yesterday and put dish together this evening. Make sure you add enough salt to your tomatillo sauce, it's just bland and not too tasty unless seasoned right. We love cilantro, so I doubled cilantro. I used the cream, but will probably leave out next time, it just made the meal very, very rich. Some reviewers commented on dullness of color. Just save some more chopped cilantro to sprinkle on top, that will perk up that dull color. Served with salad. Perfect.

